XIIGen is the application layer of the xiigen-open-llm ecosystem. xiigen-open-llm
is a planned companion repository that will hold the trainable core under the
same AGPL license; until it is published this is a described relationship, not a
link. XIIGen itself does not train model weights; it collects and cleans the
training signal and consumes ready manifests.
